            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "According to Carlisle, the court filing looks to have the Department’s 250-person limit to outdoor events applied to this gathering. Ostensibly, this measure is to curb the spread of ",
